modName: more powerful soul gems in 5 levels
summary:
changes the points for soul gems, in 5 levels, 2x 3x 4x 8x 16x.
it can be a low upgrade for people wanting it slightly better, or massive upgraded for the godmodders, 5 levels good for anyone who wants it.
